{"tid":1489093,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"老實講見到啲bno post真心覺得香港人同支那人係毫無分別","createTime":"2019-08-19T19:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T14:38:48.000Z","uid":118999,"like":32,"dislike":95,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"48ec97ceaafc299e448fe8f88721d64c1302a57c","tid":1489093,"uid":118999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:30:11.000Z","msg":"最近成人見到啲咩bno聯署，問bno點申請之類嘅post。有啲常職都知bno係無可能變bc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但只有有相關消息就會有一太堆bno撚出嚟打j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實好多出嚟嘅現屆大學生同後生仔係97或97後，坦白講佢地係無路可退出嚟死守香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />相反班97之前就抱著我有bno，真係「你有你死，我有我返屋企」<br />\n<br />\n口口聲聲話香港係我地嘅家，我地要誓死守護我地家園，結果一有機會就想走，隨便就可賣哂一齊出嚟嘅97後，真係好撚肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:97前無續bno，唔會賣隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792af7c993b5912fdd3fe0f9668b62fe3c7d133f","tid":1489093,"uid":284565,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:32:06.000Z","msg":"98 表示老豆老母想拉我走，我都唔撚走。<br />\n<br />\n小妹第四次開post了，差小小就上岸，差理科工科去過exchange，同埋文科無去過exchange 嘅現任同學仔。巴絲唔該幫幫手填個問卷......<br />\n<br />\n問卷link：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/YFTBVEyBjdxG3T4o7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FYFTBVEyBjdxG3T4o7&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex5uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=fa12c90d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/YFTBVEyBjdxG3T4o7</a><br />\n<br />\n唔想我暗地裏屌柒你比假希望我，可以睇睇指示：<br />\n<br />\n［第四次po 了］做問卷籌錢俾612 人道支援基金<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1489069\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1489069</a>"},{"pid":"a1592d5c7fc77a10d3fc04b6e9f25357c6cb004e","tid":1489093,"uid":12670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:33:22.000Z","msg":"有免費文宣啊<br />\n<br />\n［義憤民誠］地鐵報免費派十幾萬份文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488994\" da